Conway's Game of Life as written by Justin Walrath <walrathjaw@gmail.com>

If you don't know what this is: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway's_Game_of_Life

Command line arguments:
	
	--thread [threads]	Set how many threads to process the buffer with
	
	-t [Refresh time]		Set the minimum refresh time (in milliseconds)

	-g							Set the preloaded seed for glider
